le":"Reply","footer":1},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/38501.html?thread=3561317#t3561317","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/38501.html?thread=3561317#t3561317","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/38501.html?thread=3561317#t3561317","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"daintress","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://daintress.livejournal.com/","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":3561317,"talkid":13911,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/38501.html?thread=3561317#t3561317","above":3560549,"upictitle":"Daintress: Book","article":"Thank you!","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"9 years ago","ctime":"February 28 2008, 02:11:11 UTC","parent":3560549,"massactions":0,"subject":"","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://daintress.livejournal.com/","striked":null,"journaltype":"P","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/userinfo_v8.svg?v=17080?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"daintress","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":0,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"daintress","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://daintress.livejournal.com/profile","alias":0}],"dname":"daintress","ctime_ts":1204164671,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/93979269/13804587","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/38501.html?replyto=3553893","name":"reply","title":"Reply","footer":1},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/38501.html?thread=3553893#t3553893","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/38501.html?thread=3553893#t3553893","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/38501.html?thread=3553893#t3553893","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"nparisi","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://nparisi.livejournal.com/","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":3553893,"talkid":13882,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/38501.html?thread=3553893#t3553893","upictitle":"nparisi: pic#93979269","article":"George:  You mention that book editors (long form) aren't well-known to the general reading public, which brings up a question I've had for some time.  Coming from a musician's background, I've always wondered why book editors aren't credited somewhere on the book, same way a producer or engineer is credited on a record.  Has there ever been a push for this?  I honestly can't see why it would pose a problem.<br /><br />Best, Nick.","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"9 years ago","ctime":"February 25 2008, 15:10:37 UTC","massactions":0,"subject":"","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://nparisi.livejournal.com/","striked":null,"journaltype":"P","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/userinfo_v8.svg?v=17080?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"nparisi","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":0,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"nparisi","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://nparisi.livejournal.com/profile","alias":0}],"dname":"nparisi","ctime_ts":1203952237,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/27638673/967114","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/38501.html?replyto=3555173","name":"reply","title":"Reply","footer":1},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/38501.html?thread=3555173#t3555173","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/38501.html?thread=3555173#t3555173","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/38501.html?thread=3555173#t3555173","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"dd_b","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://dd-b.livejournal.com/","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":3555173,"talkid":13887,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/38501.html?thread=3555173#t3555173","above":3553893,"upictitle":"dd-b: rim-light","article":"These days, sometimes they are.  Tor books, one of the bigger SF publishers, has a policy of letting each editor decide if they want to be credited in all the books they edit, or not.  (They don't decide book-by-book because that would be too easily seen as insulting by the authors whose books they choose not to be credited in.)  So many, probably most, Tor books do credit the editor.<br /><br />I don't remember noticing that anybody else has followed them into this, yet, though.<br /><br />Sometimes you can find the editor on the acknowledgments page, too. ","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"9 years ago","ctime":"February 25 2008, 17:20:58 UTC","parent":3553893,"massactions":0,"subject":"","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://dd-b.livejournal.com/","striked":null,"journaltype":"P","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/userinfo_v8.svg?v=17080?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"dd_b","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":0,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"dd_b","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://dd-b.livejournal.com/profile","alias":0}],"dname":"dd_b","ctime_ts":1203960058,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/112939698/6348004","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/38501.html?replyto=3559525","name":"reply","title":"Reply","footer":1},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/38501.html?thread=3559525#t3559525","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/38501.html?thread=3559525#t3559525","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/38501.html?thread=3559525#t3559525","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname